text: Jane, I managed to get the training schedule for Derrick Evans. Check this out!
Monday: Cardio - 5 AM, Weights - 10 AM, Skills - 4 PM | Tuesday: Rest | Wednesday: Team Practice - 9 AM, Yoga - 7 PM...
He's also on a strict keto diet, no carbs after 7 PM, and a high-protein shake after every workout.
Make sure not to share this with too many people, it's pretty exclusive info.
